  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to the Whittaker library</i></strong>, an ancient temple that hides countless secrets and fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a young archivist who is invited to enter this mysterious library to explore the truth of those forbidden books.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/84e436d4d839eed9e2f91ccc41afe23a.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/84e436d4d839eed9e2f91ccc41afe23a.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Immersive exploration -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The delicate library scenes, atmospheric lighting and sound effects, let you feel the adventure experience of oppression and curiosity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Psychological thriller narrative -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deeply touch the dark side of human nature, explore the interweaving of memory and reality, and bring a gripping story experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Puzzle that challenges intelligence -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every book and every item in the library may be a clue. Unlock the buried secrets through observation and reasoning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/d75550c95cc10855c45b419859784975.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/d75550c95cc10855c45b419859784975.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Are you ready?</i></strong> The knowledge of Whitaker library awaits you, but the truth may cost a lot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the ranks of explorers willing to take risks and uncover the secrets behind the library!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/4363e0c4db61e2d93ecbd62565cbe782.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/4363e0c4db61e2d93ecbd62565cbe782.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=533 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to the Whittaker library</i></strong>, an ancient temple that hides countless secrets and fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a young archivist who is invited to enter this mysterious library to explore the truth of those forbidden books.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/84e436d4d839eed9e2f91ccc41afe23a.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/84e436d4d839eed9e2f91ccc41afe23a.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Immersive exploration -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The delicate library scenes, atmospheric lighting and sound effects, let you feel the adventure experience of oppression and curiosity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Psychological thriller narrative -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deeply touch the dark side of human nature, explore the interweaving of memory and reality, and bring a gripping story experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>- Puzzle that challenges intelligence -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every book and every item in the library may be a clue. Unlock the buried secrets through observation and reasoning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/d75550c95cc10855c45b419859784975.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/d75550c95cc10855c45b419859784975.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Are you ready?</i></strong> The knowledge of Whitaker library awaits you, but the truth may cost a lot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the ranks of explorers willing to take risks and uncover the secrets behind the library!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras/4363e0c4db61e2d93ecbd62565cbe782.avif?t=1746014336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384250/extras_big/4363e0c4db61e2d93ecbd62565cbe782.avif?t=1746014336 width=800 height=533 /></span></p>",
